The paper proposes a new method for Direct Volume Rendering (DVR) that focuses on simplifying the user's work by presenting only the most informative volume slices for selection. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions that the proposed method is more intuitive for medical professionals than computer scientists, indicating that the paper may also belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of a classifier, suggesting that it may belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
